{"tid":1719904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快速公路維修保養分析學術文","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:47.000Z","uid":82772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0c924acbdcf14b713dad932d35caf25160e4b58","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:54:27.000Z","msg":"各位都知道馬路維修保養係由路政署負責。當中每隔幾年就會招一次標，中標既判頭就會負責該區既維修保養事宜。<br />\n<br />\n包括但不止:<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">馬路爛左要做維修</span>(刨鋪，介打)<br />\n2. 馬路相關設施維修(防撞欄，路牌維修等等)<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">清理馬路垃圾</span>(例如提供夾車)同雨水渠保養<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: red;\">緊急時協助驚察封路</span><br />\n5. 斜坡維修<br />\n6. 做由運輸署提出既order<br />\n等等等等<br />\n<br />\n所以依啲判頭係十分重要既一環，就好似地鐵既車廠咁。<br />\n<br />\n而快速公路黎講，香港斬開東西2邊。<br />\n東面由偉金 中標<br />\n西面由中國路橋-偉金 中標<br />\n佢地都係紅底公司。<br />\n<br />\n東面負責吐露港公路，粉嶺公路，觀塘繞道，馬鞍山公路，東路走廊既維修保養。<br />\n西面就負責剩餘既公路，例如屯門公路，新田公路，西九龍走廊等等。<br />\n<br />\n當中佢地通常會設番個寫字樓/臨時地盤係附近相關地區。<br />\n以快速公路(東)黎講就會係<span style=\"color: red;\">大學站</span>附近既瑞祥街迴旋處同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">大埔大華街</span>既臨時地盤(入面會存放馬路維修相關既機械。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多先"},{"pid":"a826341610739f5aff8bcafc4eafa92ce4d57ab0","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:05:58.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"68e747f9a841286207869330dc76de0256aecc23","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"426da2c7b8a543929b694368fa6de2a6061b2c3a","tid":1719904,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"鄭立：大學係「要塞」 唔係防守而係攻擊據點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1718775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1718775</a>"},{"pid":"27934894f755312e573de6d965d5ca58e77f833e","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"1bfc5f5036d14c464088e92fb4ef718dba0071c9","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:20:08.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"d7515ea6c1a70193bf9e220010e9f1ef95dcaff2","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"feb0cd4179ac5f82cd9c70a5fb40edc092bb5bae","tid":1719904,"uid":44906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"不安"},{"pid":"7ad6539bf508cf3a4daf4bf1dc487477e92fdd08","tid":1719904,"uid":28818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"睇唔明 即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n改善空間［左膠道德撚 唔係和理非］政治唔係你做啱嘅野就會贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719977</a>"},{"pid":"479893bd23030b3f358d720526b766e736cedf66","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:33:54.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"6e02ed6e917fc9338dbcf069f81c6ef7fc2bf7ca","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"7aa3a34bdf66ad48bfa7f7d8c11940cdb3d05cc4","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"e559940aa5367e5cb47a2ed08de6e7bb0ed543a5","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"8565653e38333ee60e882ce417247f09353a6b5c","tid":1719904,"uid":82772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"自推10 收皮"}]}